{"tid":1353783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「五大訴求」緊要啲，定光復元朗緊要啲？","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:16:00.000Z","uid":278053,"like":37,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0d646fb09c7418ddb03f0abfee59dbb07b6f37","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"331&gt;428&gt;&gt;&gt;69&gt;612&gt;616&gt;71&gt;77&gt;714&gt;721<br />\n尖沙咀23萬，沙田11萬，到港島明明有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">43萬人</span></strong></span>出嚟呀！<br />\n夜晚中上西環仲有血腥鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />催淚煙橡膠彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但同612果陣嘅noise比，<br />\n721成件事好似冇發生過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家主流媒體定香討babykingdom，，<br />\n以至係最愛国愛港嘅連登，<br />\n都仲係煲緊元朗警黑單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單係唔可以唔理！<br />\n係呀我都好嬲呀，，但係希望大家記住呢啲都只不過係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">副線</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主線係咩呀？</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求係咩呀</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「撤回逃犯條例」<br />\n「撤回暴動定義」<br />\n「撤回所有抗爭者控罪」<br />\n「追究警隊濫權」<br />\n「立即實行雙普選」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無論做咩都好都唔好失焦！不分化不割席！<br />\n但老土講句<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做任何嘢之前都要三思</span></strong>！<br />\n嚟緊光復元朗有人話夢見燒村掘墳，<br />\n令我諗起有個呀太打上電台勸年輕人，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做完令你洩憤令你越爽嘅野只會令你跌得越快</span></span></strong><br />\n啱啱睇到有巴打講，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好唔記得中共最叻拉一派打一派</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由最初69，612，616果期訴求好清晰，<br />\n但到衍生左唔同副線出嚟，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再加上西環出手，私煙果堆又出番嚟揾食，<br />\n就好明顯有人想溝淡主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係呀，新城市，元朗警黑，何妖呢啲令人好嬲，呢啲事都要追究唔可以忘記但記住呢啲都只係成場反送中裡面嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">副線</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家要打大佬呀，唔好掛住撚啲𡃁先得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"14c77ed6a2ad3419e62f4af12fb7b0575302520b","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"整合返其他巴打嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《連登已被五毛滲透 拉緊風向去內鬥》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351639/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351639/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n咁大穫無人講? ７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351301/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351301/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f62970b9a4bf5e82c675a416e9b68f0db2884fa3","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"298f478e182f62c2ea506548f52e74d185bb5862","tid":1353783,"uid":272976,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀，你唔解支線點觸發主線<br />\n幾多兄弟出完去返屋企俾鄉黑打，你當兄弟係condom？"},{"pid":"b34a12bc184d7a0cb009d5a4fa1d521e923cc5a8","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"[深夜閒談]話721上環留守係「送頭」果班冷氣軍師 根本冇理解過前線既理念係咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1352395/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1352395/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bf456a5988ff3843c37fd194736edc906c3d8ca1","tid":1353783,"uid":274734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"所以，元朗都要做，提升集氣力量"},{"pid":"b3e1e736ddd3799645b7a668e82490dda4ba8d79","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"298f478e182f62c2ea506548f52e74d185bb5862","tid":1353783,"uid":272976,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀，你唔解支線點觸發主線<br />\n幾多兄弟出完去返屋企俾鄉黑打，你當兄弟係condom？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"冇話過唔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係驚妹仔大過主人婆，<br />\n拉一派打一派呀，<br />\n真正我地要對付嘅係鄊黑定政府呀？？"},{"pid":"1588a2c867ed234545295a6962db6604f436d5b9","tid":1353783,"uid":30006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"元朗係就五大訴求最後一關<br />\n<br />\n你可以咁理解<br />\n<br />\n不可分割兩間事<br />\n<br />\n政府連黑都無用，一係出老解一係跪"},{"pid":"62a5c97e78a48d3de66b78a403e1193f4261115a","tid":1353783,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 必不可少"},{"pid":"641c116c1ede68894d7bbaa227b65a74dc3b1ac6","tid":1353783,"uid":148332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"變成6大訴求咪得"},{"pid":"22452aa7d9a6ff48cd5a3a29b2c82a19f05e4930","tid":1353783,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"屯元天佔1/6人口，唔幫元朗，第日五大訴求遊行只會更加少人出"},{"pid":"c338fed1f46a30e1d02ee82620765290a1aa3ec5","tid":1353783,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"南邊圍村P牌仔?<br />\n<br />\n今次南邊圍鄉黑玩恐怖襲擊, 無差別傷害市民<br />\n<br />\n無得拆架啦！"},{"pid":"825211785147173d4d8d71b1cdeef93609f92ab2","tid":1353783,"uid":278053,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c338fed1f46a30e1d02ee82620765290a1aa3ec5","tid":1353783,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":